videos.headline: Sanders airs it out to Stoner for a 57-yard TD
videos.description: Oklahoma State's Spencer Sanders avoids the pressure and throws to a wide-open Dillon Stoner for a 57-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sanders airs it out to Stoner for a 57-yard TD) 2019/11/2

videos.headline: Stoner hauls in an amazing TD for Oklahoma State
videos.description: Spencer Sanders throws a fantastic pass to Dillon Stoner, who makes an even better catch while falling to the ground for a 22-yard Oklahoma State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stoner hauls in an amazing TD for Oklahoma State) 2019/11/2

videos.headline: Reagor leaps to make dynamic catch for TCU
videos.description: Jalen Reagor leaps up and goes full extension to haul in a fantastic 37-yard catch for TCU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Reagor leaps to make dynamic catch for TCU) 2019/11/2

videos.headline: Johnson makes unbelievable catch for Oklahoma State
videos.description: Braydon Johnson gets separation from his defenders and hauls in a heck of a catch while falling to the ground for a 47-yard reception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnson makes unbelievable catch for Oklahoma State) 2019/11/2

videos.headline: Hubbard goes off to the races for a 62-yard TD
videos.description: Chuba Hubbard runs in another long touchdown, this time going 62 yards to increase Oklahoma State's lead over TCU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hubbard goes off to the races for a 62-yard TD) 2019/11/2
